299
00:17:26,671 --> 00:17:30,550
<i>Três minutos restantes</i>
<i>para o acionamento manual do soma.</i>

300
00:17:32,051 --> 00:17:33,261
Vamos, rápido.

301
00:17:38,724 --> 00:17:39,559
Niko?

302
00:17:40,851 --> 00:17:42,436
